{"tid":634243,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[上環JJ]有咩平野食推介","createTime":"2018-04-19T04:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T10:52:03.000Z","uid":75735,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"875109c9210ee2e3025f92982fed31e12009522a","tid":634243,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"岩岩換左工係上環番<br />\n頭幾日都禮貌上同老細同事social下<br />\n餐餐lunch都食成舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家終於可以做番小毒撚<br />\n想問向位上環JJ有咩好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實超多餐廳 多到唔知食咩好先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時我試左生記魚湯米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fdbda8467d9423e6942fe8405f658b98442229","tid":634243,"uid":9974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"上環熟食中心"},{"pid":"593e6e7198a8d33095975735b16b71a369c5d805","tid":634243,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"大飯桶<br />\n上環食堂"},{"pid":"4ba4f61b88176b888ae5486bb0e9a97da25cd97c","tid":634243,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29fdbda8467d9423e6942fe8405f658b98442229","tid":634243,"uid":9974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"上環熟食中心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"今日試左家和燒魚<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff041166737fdbe2404b85dd15f017ac1d7bc77b","tid":634243,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"593e6e7198a8d33095975735b16b71a369c5d805","tid":634243,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"大飯桶<br />\n上環食堂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"食堂成日經過都想試<br />\n大飯桶係食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"