plyTime":"2018-04-19T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"大飯桶<br />\n上環食堂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"食堂成日經過都想試<br />\n大飯桶係食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"兩餸飯"},{"pid":"f78da4f17564f81549f4e5e20865d2bfc2d9627b","tid":634243,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0023ec2bf9259f566a9aa76dd9ddc7c6fb2944e","tid":634243,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ba4f61b88176b888ae5486bb0e9a97da25cd97c","tid":634243,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29fdbda8467d9423e6942fe8405f658b98442229","tid":634243,"uid":9974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"上環熟食中心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"今日試左家和燒魚<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:18:50.000Z","msg":"多唔多人？咩鐘數？搵日想試，有無菜式推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T20:10:13.000Z","msg":"我點半去食<br />\n應該撞正其他OL番歸 有好多位<br />\n<br />\n我無試好多野 冇稔住豪食<br />\n叫左條鹽燒馬尤 <br />\n50蚊 跟飯 幾條醃青瓜 面屎湯(我見同台阿叔係咁自己走去refill 唔知係咪佢熟客先比佢咁)<br />\n<br />\n基本上就係一條魚 點豉油 送飯食<br />\n唔知你會唔會覺得好寡<br />\n我一開始見到係覺<br />\n但條魚堅係好正<br />\n送飯一流<br />\n<br />\n但前提係要鐘意食魚<br />\n<br />\n其他野食唔清楚<br />\n但我見都好多人叫<br />\n或者等巴打介紹<br />\n<br />\n有樣好奇怪<br />\n我落完單 唔夠兩分鐘就送左上黎<br />\n叫得燒魚都預左要等<br />\n寧願佢燒得好食<br />\n依間明顯係會燒住等客<br />\n好奇在即使係咁燒既時間仍然岩岩好<br />\n如果唔係我咁好彩食到條嫩魚<br />\n咁就係依間鋪頭掌握火候好撚勁"},{"pid":"99580641bd4a67259e9822b1222d232925fed941","tid":634243,"uid":26003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T20:19:10.000Z","msg":"新森林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a713ffa9cf394a8cd40765d0397c43f715d6a9","tid":634243,"uid":155720,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T20:21:55.000Z","msg":"咪咪茶餐廳，啲飯煮到一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6632157e418fa64807b6b3cf396421e8a6f500f7","tid":634243,"uid":56307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a713ffa9cf394a8cd40765d0397c43f715d6a9","tid":634243,"uid":155720,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T20:21:55.000Z","msg":"咪咪茶餐廳，啲飯煮到一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"咪咪個牛腩飯好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315067e490121cc64ecf9a30825049538ed03016","tid":634243,"uid":83328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99580641bd4a67259e9822b1222d232925fed941","tid":634243,"uid":26003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T20:19:10.000Z","msg":"新森林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696e21339b4c4355a964b29a8b79eba8817c2ecc","tid":634243,"uid":6562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6632157e418fa64807b6b3cf396421e8a6f500f7","tid":634243,"uid":56307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a713ffa9cf394a8cd40765d0397c43f715d6a9","tid":634243,"uid":155720,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T20:21:55.000Z","msg":"咪咪茶餐廳，啲飯煮到一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"咪咪個牛腩飯好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"咪咪好撚污糟.... <br />\n飯都好D 任何湯/湯面都盡量唔好叫啦...<br />\n試過兩次同事食都有甲由..雖然味道係幾好<br />\n上環熟食中心的確正 上面講左<br />\n日之苑外賣我都覺得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n糧尾要平 食下權記粉面都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi